text.section:
The notice of a claim shall contain:
evidence that the claimant:
has fulfilled all requirements to file a claim; and
is not eligible for uninsured motorist coverage benefits from a policy issued to the claimant or a family member who resides in the claimant's household;
certification by the claimant's employer of all lost wages incurred up to the filing of notice of a claim;
evidence of all medical expenses incurred up to the filing of notice of a claim;
all reports of medical treatment and consultation for injuries sustained;
evidence of all other damages claimed up to the filing of the notice of claim;
all available police or other accident reports; and
additional information that the Executive Director requires by regulation.
